{
  "title": "Xtra Nutty Algerian White Beans Tagine",
  "description": "A nutty and creamy Algerian dish featuring dried white beans and ferment-jang, perfect for a festive dinner. This egg-free-friendly recipe is cooked to perfection in a kadhai.",
